00:00:05.795 --> 00:00:06.953
that worked well for him.

00:00:06.953 --> 00:00:10.103
A poetic form congenial to Robert Browning

00:00:10.103 --> 00:00:12.547
was the dramatic monologue.

00:00:12.980 --> 00:00:15.641
It let him explore a character's mind

00:00:15.641 --> 00:00:17.855
without the simplifications demanded

00:00:17.855 --> 00:00:19.496
by stage productions.

