00:00:24.195 --> 00:00:26.022
If I really read it
actually with the comma,

00:00:26.022 --> 00:00:27.933
it would have been "A
poetic form congenial

00:00:27.933 --> 00:00:30.270
"to Robert Browning was
the dramatic monologue,

00:00:30.270 --> 00:00:31.997
